    <briefdescription>
<para>Restricts a value so it stays within a specified range. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Internally uses Mathf.Clamp. If the value is less than the minimum it returns the minimum. If the value is greater than the maximum it returns the maximum. Otherwise the value is returned unchanged. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
